                "title": "Minimum Wage Requirements",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "data": "The minimum wage in Honduras is complex. The minimum wage is dependent on the number of employees at a company and the type of work carried out. For Deel, the most relevant size and activity will be HNL 10,008.14-13,346.47 per month."
                    }
                ]
